    "description": "<strong>Tatari </strong>是一款第一人称冒险游戏，玩家将扮演一名被派来处理失踪案件的侦探。作为一名警探，你被派往失踪者最后出现的地点进行调查。在那里，你经历一些你的逻辑思维似乎无法理解的超自然行为。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847420/extras/edac19f26e5023d08e5423150795eac7.poster.avif?t=1768555032\" width=618 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847420/extras/edac19f26e5023d08e5423150795eac7.webm?t=1768555032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847420/extras/edac19f26e5023d08e5423150795eac7.mp4?t=1768555032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你将根据证据来到一个荒废多年的村庄，那里埋藏着许多关于那个案件的秘密和细节。所有可能有用的地方都布满了谜题和门锁，你的目标就是打开这些谜题和锁，获取遗忘和隐藏的信息，让你更接近案件的结局。不过要小心，有些谜题比它们看起来更困难，可能会让你付出生命的代价。请谨慎行事。Tatari 根据日本都市传说改编，你将亲身体验这一故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847420/extras/6f4e3b8e7f2d33093bf882ee9bb3903c.poster.avif?t=1768555032\" width=618 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847420/extras/6f4e3b8e7f2d33093bf882ee9bb3903c.webm?t=1768555032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847420/extras/6f4e3b8e7f2d33093bf882ee9bb3903c.mp4?t=1768555032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
